स्व॒र॒वि॒ष॒ये (सि॑द्धान्तकौमु॒द्याः स्व॑रप्रकर॒णम्, https://drdhaval2785.github.io/siddhantakaumudi/#SK3650) अथ॑ (स्वरसिद्धान्तचन्द्रि॒का, https://archive.org/details/Svara-Siddhanta-Chandrika-Of-Srinivasa-Yajva-Sivaramakrishna-Sastri-1936-Annamalai-University) च॑ स्तः। अथ॑ चा॒नयोः॒ कोश॑योः ब॒हवः॒ शब्दाः॒ सस्व॑राः॒ सञ्चि॑ताः। (पी॒ट॒र्त्स्ब॒र्क्को॒शः, https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/PWGScan/2020/web/index.php)। (मो॒नि॒य॒र्वि॒लि॒य॒ङ्को॒श, https://www.sanskrit-lexicon.uni-koeln.de/scans/MWScan/2020/web/index.php) आ॑ङ्ग्लभा॒षाया॑म्।
